Test Plan
Website : Saucedemo - https://www.saucedemo.com/ 
1.	Purpose
The purpose of the Swag Labs website is to provide an online platform where users can view, select, and order available products. 
2. Project scope:
Login: Verification of valid and invalid parameters.
Main Page: Verification of product images, prices, product information.
Filtering: Filtering products by name and price.
Burger Menu: Verification of all menu items, including About, Log Out, and Reset App State options.
Cart Functionality: Adding products to the cart, removing products from the cart, proceeding to checkout, and returning to the main page.
Contact: Verification of social media links (LinkedIn, Facebook, Twitter).

3.	Types of Testing
•	Functional testing
•	Non - Functional testing: 
•	Performance testing (load testing)
•	UI\ UX Testing
•       Cross Browser testing 

4. Entry Criteria

The website is accessible.
Test cases are prepared in Qase.io.
Login credentials are available.

Exit Criteria 
All planned test cases are executed.
Critical bugs are fixed or reported.
Test results are documented.
Testing is completed within the deadline.

4.	Test Environment
•	Browser: Chrome Version 143.0.7499.194
•	OS: Windows 10

5.	Test Team
•	Gunel Babayeva - QA Engineer

6.	Deadline
•	19.01.2026 – 23.01.2026

7.	Risks
•	Some functions are not tested.



